-- 鏄嗗北浣版嘲鑳滀笓灞?ERP 路 鏁版嵁搴撲竴閿垵濮嬪寲锛堢┖搴撲笓鐢級
-- 搴撳悕锛歝nc_platform / cnc_business / cnc_production
-- 鐢ㄦ硶锛歮ysql -h HOST -u USER -p --default-character-set=utf8mb4 < backend/db/init.sql
-- 缁存姢锛氭敼 init.baseline.sql 鎴?migrations 鍚庢墽琛?build-init.ps1
